[header]Feeling Off This Shift?[/header]
[b]Talk to the Station Psychologist[/b]

Stress, trauma, burnout, paranoia — these aren't just "in your head." They're real, and they [i]can[/i] be treated.

Whether you've had a rough shift, lost a limb, or can't sleep after that last anomaly breach, [b]confidential psychological support is available.[/b]
Even cronic problems like narcolepsy, can be treated.

• Private, judgment-free sessions  
• [b]Medication available when needed[/b]  
• Walk-ins or referrals accepted  
• No cameras. No AI. No records without your consent.

[i]Located next to Medbay. Just knock.[/i]  
Your mind deserves as much care as your body.
